{"tid":1885994,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"( 社評 ) 任何明顯 挑釁/挑撥/分化/無聊 topic 既 post 唔使覆, 唔使理，由佢沉, 正負評都唔須要。","createTime":"2020-02-18T16:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T21:45:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2a47554de2e519c594c763008bba56e73c3dc680","tid":1885994,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"( 社評 ) 任何明顯 挑釁/挑撥/分化/無聊 topic 既 post 唔使覆, 唔使理，由佢沉, 正負評都唔須要。<br />\n<br />\n無謂變相幫助推呢類 post 洗版。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">真係忍唔到要覆既, 就用不推文回覆</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">無謂畀個標題浮面。</span><br />\n<br />\n----------------<br />\n<br />\n收到！ 標題同內文都會review<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n--------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">其實最好都係唔好覆， 由佢沉。</span><br />\n<br />\n因為就算你用 不推文回覆 覆咗個 post,<br />\n佢就有機會用 推文回覆 咋啼駁你，<br />\n咁個 post 又有機會浮返面。"},{"pid":"88c73bf9562d4b28258099f46699c40d20817982","tid":1885994,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"21/2/2020(五)<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">元朗</span></span>恐襲七個月 靜坐<br />\n<br />\n時間：19:30<br />\n地點：元朗黨鐵站/Yoho Mall<br />\n自備：口罩 文宣<br />\n<br />\n#21FEB20 #元朗 #七二一 #集會 #靜坐 #新界西<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAyupn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAyupn5.jpg&h=bbdb7892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n21/2/2020(五)<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港仔</span></span> 勿忘721．七個月靜坐<br />\n<br />\n時間：20:00<br />\n地點：香港仔中心<br />\n自備：口罩 文宣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/southern_scout/6130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsouthern_scout%2F6130&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=4a8d2e94\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/southern_scout/6130</a><br />\n<br />\n#21FEB20 #香港仔 #七二一 #集會 #靜坐 #港島<b